{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-basis-property-to-set-the-initial-size-of-an-item","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-flexbox","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi svojstvo `flex-basis` za postavljanje početne veličine elementa","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Atribut <code>flex-basis</code> opisuje početnu veličinu elementa pre nego što CSS izvrši izmene na <code>flex-shrink</code> ili <code>flex-grow</code>.</p>\n<p>Dimenzije koje se koriste sa svojstvom <code>flex-basis</code> su jednake drugim svojstvima veličine (<code>px</code>, <code>em</code>, <code>%</code>, itd.). Vrednost <code>auto</code> određuje veličinu komponenti u zavisnosti od sadržaja.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d78ae367417b2b2512afd","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Postavite početnu veličinu kutija koristeći <code>flex-basis</code>. Dodajte atribut CSS <code>flex-basis</code> za <code>#box-1</code> na <code>#box-2</code>. Navedite <code>#box-1</code> sa vrednošću <code>10em</code> i <code>#box-2</code> sa vrednošću <code>20em</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pVaDAv/c3d9nCa","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301108,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-basis-property-to-set-the-initial-size-of-an-item"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  #box-container {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  #box-1 {\r\n    background-color: dodgerblue;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  #box-2 {\r\n    background-color: orangered;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"box-container\">\r\n  <div id=\"box-1\"></div>\r\n  <div id=\"box-2\"></div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Komponenta <code>#box-1</code> mora imati svojstvo <code>flex-basis</code>.</p>","testString":"const boxOne = document.querySelector('#box-1');\r\nconst flexBasis = window.getComputedStyle(boxOne)['flex-basis'];\r\nassert.notStrictEqual(flexBasis, 'auto');"},{"text":"<p>Polje za <code>#box-1</code> mora imati vrednost <code>flex-basis</code> od <code>10em</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /#box-1\\s*?{\\s*?.*?\\s*?.*?\\s*?flex-basis:\\s*?10em;/g);"},{"text":"<p>Element od <code>#box-2</code> treba da ima svojstvo <code>flex-basis</code>.</p>","testString":"const boxTwo = document.querySelector('#box-2');\r\nconst flexBasis = window.getComputedStyle(boxTwo)['flex-basis'];\r\nassert.notStrictEqual(flexBasis, 'auto');"},{"text":"<p>Element <code>#box-2</code> treba da ima vrednost <code>flex-basis</code> od <code>20em</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /#box-2\\s*?{\\s*?.*?\\s*?.*?\\s*?flex-basis:\\s*?20em;/g);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-flexbox","dashedName":"use-the-flex-basis-property-to-set-the-initial-size-of-an-item","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-flexbox","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-shorthand-property","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-grow-property-to-expand-items","id":"587d78ae367417b2b2512afd","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\r\n  #box-container {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n  }\r\n  #box-1 {\r\n    background-color: dodgerblue;\r\n    align-self: center;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n    width: 200px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  #box-2 {\r\n    background-color: orangered;\r\n    align-self: flex-end;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n    width: 200px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"box-container\">\r\n  <div id=\"box-1\"></div>\r\n  <div id=\"box-2\"></div>\r\n</div>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-basis-property-to-set-the-initial-size-of-an-item"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}